headline: Why Moderna (MRNA) Stock Is Trading Lower Today
summary: Shares of biotechnology company Moderna (NASDAQ:MRNA) fell 3.5% in the afternoon session after the stock retreated, giving back some of the strong gains from the previous session that were fueled by reports of potential buyout or partnership discussions.
